1
00:00:06,760 --> 00:00:10,960
- Harry's at the hospital...
- Mhm...

2
00:00:11,060 --> 00:00:14,540
Daddy Axel is sleeping at the hospital with Harry.

3
00:00:14,620 --> 00:00:18,960
If you follow our instagram (the_swedish_family),
you probably know this already.

4
00:00:19,000 --> 00:00:23,600
