Watch CKN Toys.
Could you tell our viewers what that is?

68
00:05:49,300 --> 00:05:53,220
It's a person opening toys.

69
00:05:53,580 --> 00:05:56,040
- It's a child, right?
- Yes.

70
00:05:56,040 --> 00:05:58,520
Well, a child is also a person...

71
00:05:58,520 --> 00:06:02,000
Should he get to watch CKN Toys?

72
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:06,680
Yes, for a little bit. One episode.

73
00:06:07,520 --> 00:06:09,780
Three episodes.

74
00:06:10,640 --> 00:06:13,580
- Daddy, three episodes?
- One.

75
00:06:13,960 --> 00:06:16,200
- No, three?
- One.

76
00:06:16,320 --> 00:06:18,400
Okay, two then.

77
00:06:19,600 --> 00:06:21,500
Tough negotiation...

78
00:06:22,100 --> 00:06:28,720
I'll pick up Alma, then we might come back here,
so she can see Harry.

79
00:06:28,760 --> 00:06:31,160
They miss each other quite a lot.

80
00:06:32,440 --> 00:06:37,900
Harry, the nurse said you're getting an ultrasound now.

81
00:06:50,880 --> 00:06:55,780
We're waiting for the doctor,
and Harry's watching a movie.

82
00:06:55,900 --> 00:06:59,980
I don't think we'll be able to film during the procedure.

83
00:07:01,460 --> 00:07:04,060
We're back in our room.

84
00:07:05,880 --> 00:07:08,380
How did the procedure go, Harry?

85
00:07:08,740 --> 00:07:10,080
Well.

86
00:07:10,440 --> 00:07:14,000
Was it uncomfortable to get
the wet stuff smeared on your belly?

87
00:07:14,000 --> 00:07:14,980
Yes.

88
00:07:15,300 --> 00:07:24,820
