91
00:07:31,260 --> 00:07:35,360
- We're waiting for...
- I'm sleeping here again?

92
00:07:35,360 --> 00:07:41,120
We don't know. We're waiting for information
on whether you can go home, or need to stay.

93
00:07:46,540 --> 00:07:49,920
I'll get sick if I finish this.

94
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:57,800
You've already finished it!

95
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:02,180
Great!

96
00:08:02,880 --> 00:08:07,440
Harry hasn't eaten much today. Almost only an apple.

97
00:08:07,660 --> 00:08:12,140
Now he finished this nutritional energy drink.

98
00:08:12,140 --> 00:08:16,200
- Look, there's a dinosaur on it!
- Yes.

99
00:08:16,200 --> 00:08:19,340
That means you'll get big and strong like a dino!

100
00:08:20,720 --> 00:08:25,360
Do you remember what you get to do
now that you've finished your drink?

101
00:08:25,360 --> 00:08:26,780
- No. 
- You don't?

102
00:08:26,780 --> 00:08:29,380
- The stickers!
- That's right!

103
00:08:30,060 --> 00:08:38,080
Harry got this book where you put stickers
when you've eaten and drunk.

104
00:08:38,820 --> 00:08:41,780
Can you see if you can find what you just drank?

105
00:08:41,780 --> 00:08:43,580
There it is.

106
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:45,880
